content.rendered:
A former American Marine who is struggling with a dissociative identity disorder is endowed with the power of an Egyptian moon god. However, he soon realizes that these newly acquired powers can be both a blessing and a curse in his troubled life.

Seasons: 1 (2022)

Status: Finished

Creator: Doug Moench

Channel: Disney

Starring: Oscar Isaac, Ethan Hawke, May Calamawy
